Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./Material/lebo113.pdf
------Bio12Boundary--


### 8.2  Ingest book — mismatched PDF count (expect 422)
POST {{base}}/admin/ingest-book
X-Admin-Key: {{admin_key}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----MismatchBoundary

------MismatchBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Mismatch Test Book
------MismatchBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="grade"

12
------MismatchBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="subject"

biology
------MismatchBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="chapters"

[{"number":1,"title":"Chapter One"},{"number":2,"title":"Chapter Two"}]
------MismatchBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="pdfs"; filename="lebo101.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./Material/lebo101.pdf
------MismatchBoundary--


### 8.3  Ingest book — invalid chapters JSON (expect 422)
POST {{base}}/admin/ingest-book
X-Admin-Key: {{admin_key}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----BadJsonBoundary

------BadJsonBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Bad JSON Test
------BadJsonBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="grade"

12
------BadJsonBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="subject"

biology
------BadJsonBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="chapters"

not valid json at all
------BadJsonBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="pdfs"; filename="lebo101.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./Material/lebo101.pdf
------BadJsonBoundary--


# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 9 ── POST-INGEST SMOKE TESTS  (fill @bio12_chapter_id first)
# ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 9.1  SRS — ask about Ch.1 (Reproduction in Organisms)
POST {{base}}/srs/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question":   "What are the different modes of asexual reproduction found in animals? Give two examples for each.",
  "chapter_id": "{{bio12_chapter_id}}"
}


### 9.2  SRS — ask about genetics
POST {{base}}/srs/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question":   "Explain Mendel's law of segregation with an example.",
  "chapter_id": "{{bio12_chapter_id}}"
}


### 9.3  MindMap — nested tree for the ingested chapter
# @name bio12_mindmap
GET {{base}}/mindmap/{{bio12_chapter_id}}
Accept: application/json


### 9.4  MindMap — flat node list (React-Flow format)
GET {{base}}/mindmap/{{bio12_chapter_id}}/flat
Accept: application/json
